00:37:24.240 --> 00:37:28.340 align:middle line:10%
house who thought she was
electrically sensitive just

00:37:28.340 --> 00:37:30.430 align:middle line:10%
to try and help her
and to explain to her

00:37:30.430 --> 00:37:32.280 align:middle line:10%
what electrical
sensitivity was and what

00:37:32.280 --> 00:37:33.880 align:middle line:10%
might be causing her problem.

00:37:33.880 --> 00:37:36.090 align:middle line:84%
And to make a long story
