00:37:36.090 --> 00:37:38.130 align:middle line:84%
that this particular
lady had a problem

00:37:38.130 --> 00:37:40.610 align:middle line:84%
but she was not
electrically sensitive.

00:37:40.610 --> 00:37:43.980 align:middle line:84%
She was definitely not
electrically sensitive.

00:37:43.980 --> 00:37:46.440 align:middle line:84%
But in the going of
the conversation,

00:37:46.440 --> 00:37:50.180 align:middle line:84%
she'd signed up for
the Essex trials

00:37:50.180 --> 00:37:53.970 align:middle line:84%
to try and find out whether
she was electrically sensitive.

00:37:53.970 --> 00:37:55.345 align:middle line:90%
Well, my heart missed a beat.

00:37:55.345 --> 00:37:58.400 align:middle line:84%
Well, here's somebody that's
not electrically sensitive

00:37:58.400 --> 00:38:02.340 align:middle line:84%
