00:54:17.320 --> 00:54:18.110 align:middle line:90%
and using the phone.

00:54:18.110 --> 00:54:38.258 align:middle line:90%


00:54:38.258 --> 00:54:41.030 align:middle line:84%
NARRATOR: It's hard to
imagine a piece of technology

00:54:41.030 --> 00:54:42.930 align:middle line:84%
which has accelerated
into our lives

00:54:42.930 --> 00:54:44.236 align:middle line:90%
quite like the mobile phone.

00:54:44.236 --> 00:54:47.240 align:middle line:90%


00:54:47.240 --> 00:54:50.342 align:middle line:84%
25 years ago, it was seen as
little more than a gimmick.

00:54:50.342 --> 00:54:54.040 align:middle line:90%


00:54:54.040 --> 00:55:01.010 align:middle line:84%
