00:55:03.630 --> 00:55:04.869 align:middle line:90%
is just eight years old.

00:55:04.869 --> 00:55:09.090 align:middle line:90%


00:55:09.090 --> 00:55:11.470 align:middle line:84%
The way a mobile phone
works is by sending

00:55:11.470 --> 00:55:13.180 align:middle line:84%
and receiving
microwave frequencies

00:55:13.180 --> 00:55:16.090 align:middle line:90%
to and from the bay station.

00:55:16.090 --> 00:55:18.940 align:middle line:84%
So having a phone pressed
against your head inevitably

00:55:18.940 --> 00:55:23.900 align:middle line:84%
means your brain is being
exposed to those waves.

00:55:23.900 --> 00:55:27.630 align:middle line:84%
Does the brain react
to this exposure?

00:55:27.630 --> 00:55:33.890 align:middle line:84%
A recent American study
shows it absolutely does.

00:55:33.890 --> 00:55:37.540 align:middle line:84%
The work was carried
out by Dr. Nora Volkow.

00:55:37.540 --> 00:55:40.740 align:middle line:84%
Dr. Volkow and her team
studied 47 healthy people

00:55:40.740 --> 00:55:43.090 align:middle line:90%
for an entire year.

00:55:43.090 --> 00:55:45.660 align:middle line:84%
Participants had a cell phone
placed on their left and right

00:55:45.660 --> 00:55:49.510 align:middle line:84%
ears, one was
activated but muted,

00:55:49.510 --> 00:55:51.660 align:middle line:90%
the other was turned off.

00:55:51.660 --> 00:55:54.800 align:middle line:84%
Dr. Volkow used brain
imaging equipment

00:55:54.800 --> 00:55:56.570 align:middle line:84%
to study how much
glucose the brain

00:55:56.570 --> 00:55:57.811 align:middle line:90%
would use during exposure.

00:55:57.811 --> 00:56:01.490 align:middle line:90%


00:56:01.490 --> 00:56:04.890 align:middle line:10%
So it's a very sensitive
marker to indicate if there are

00:56:04.890 --> 00:56:07.610 align:middle line:10%
changes in brain
activity that may

00:56:07.610 --> 00:56:10.720 align:middle line:10%
be driven by a given
stimulus, which in this case

00:56:10.720 --> 00:56:12.030 align:middle line:10%
was the cell phone.

00:56:12.030 --> 00:56:14.796 align:middle line:90%


00:56:14.796 --> 00:56:16.760 align:middle line:84%
NARRATOR: When the
brain is stimulated,

00:56:16.760 --> 00:56:22.270 align:middle line:84%
it consumes glucose in the
same way a car consumes fuel.

00:56:22.270 --> 00:56:25.750 align:middle line:84%
50-minutes exposure
to a cell phone

00:56:25.750 --> 00:56:29.490 align:middle line:84%
was associated with increases
in glucose consumption

00:56:29.490 --> 00:56:31.890 align:middle line:84%
by the brain, which
indicates that the brain

00:56:31.890 --> 00:56:35.030 align:middle line:84%
was being activated by
the radio frequencies

00:56:35.030 --> 00:56:36.090 align:middle line:90%
from the cell phone.

00:56:36.090 --> 00:56:37.670 align:middle line:84%
This right area
of the brain that

00:56:37.670 --> 00:56:41.000 align:middle line:84%
was very close to the
antenna show the largest

00:56:41.000 --> 00:56:43.700 align:middle line:84%
increases in
metabolism as compare

00:56:43.700 --> 00:56:45.363 align:middle line:90%
when the telephones were off.

00:56:45.363 --> 00:56:49.530 align:middle line:90%


00:56:49.530 --> 00:56:52.490 align:middle line:84%
Even though the radio
frequencies that are emitted

00:56:52.490 --> 00:56:55.880 align:middle line:84%
from current cell phone
technologies are very weak,

00:56:55.880 --> 00:57:01.042 align:middle line:84%
they are able to activate the
human brain, to have an effect.

00:57:01.042 --> 00:57:03.350 align:middle line:84%
NARRATOR: By using
a muted cell phone,

00:57:03.350 --> 00:57:06.900 align:middle line:84%
Dr. Volkow's experiment showed
that the human brain has

00:57:06.900 --> 00:57:09.010 align:middle line:84%
a metabolic reaction to
the presence of microwaves

00:57:09.010 --> 00:57:13.400 align:middle line:84%
from a mobile phone, a
metabolic reaction at levels

00:57:13.400 --> 00:57:17.650 align:middle line:84%
well below the legal limit,
something many people

00:57:17.650 --> 00:57:20.135 align:middle line:90%
claimed was impossible.

00:57:20.135 --> 00:57:24.830 align:middle line:90%


00:57:24.830 --> 00:57:26.790 align:middle line:84%
And the reaction
recorded by the doctor

00:57:26.790 --> 00:57:30.860 align:middle line:84%
is secondary to an even
greater concern, the way

00:57:30.860 --> 00:57:35.650 align:middle line:84%
that those microwaves are
actually absorbed by the brain.

00:57:35.650 --> 00:57:38.010 align:middle line:90%
This has become known as SAR.

00:57:38.010 --> 00:57:46.820 align:middle line:90%


00:57:46.820 --> 00:57:50.060 align:middle line:10%
SAR is, well, first of all, it
stands for specific absorption

00:57:50.060 --> 00:57:56.680 align:middle line:10%
rate and that's the measure of
how much RF energy in this case

00:57:56.680 --> 00:57:59.570 align:middle line:10%
radio waves is absorbed
into the human body

00:57:59.570 --> 00:58:03.350 align:middle line:10%
over a certain period of
time within a certain volume.

00:58:03.350 --> 00:58:05.620 align:middle line:10%
So it's a measure of
the heating effect

00:58:05.620 --> 00:58:08.180 align:middle line:10%
that a radio transmitter
would have on your body,

00:58:08.180 --> 00:58:10.685 align:middle line:10%
on the human body.

00:58:10.685 --> 00:58:12.420 align:middle line:84%
NARRATOR: The SAR for
every mobile phone

00:58:12.420 --> 00:58:15.610 align:middle line:84%
is measured in this way,
using an artificial head

00:58:15.610 --> 00:58:18.160 align:middle line:90%
called a SAM phantom.

00:58:18.160 --> 00:58:20.000 align:middle line:84%
This is filled with
a glucose mixture

00:58:20.000 --> 00:58:22.990 align:middle line:90%
which represents the brain.

00:58:22.990 --> 00:58:25.630 align:middle line:84%
The probe measures the
amount of microwave radiation

00:58:25.630 --> 00:58:30.250 align:middle line:84%
that penetrates the
SAM phantom skull

00:58:30.250 --> 00:58:32.240 align:middle line:84%
and calculates a
SAR rating based

00:58:32.240 --> 00:58:33.640 align:middle line:90%
on how much energy is absorbed.

00:58:33.640 --> 00:58:39.690 align:middle line:90%


00:58:39.690 --> 00:58:43.120 align:middle line:84%
From the European Union, the
limit is 2 watts per kilogram,

00:58:43.120 --> 00:58:45.890 align:middle line:90%
over 10 gram average of tissue.

00:58:45.890 --> 00:58:48.270 align:middle line:84%
For America, it's 1.6
watts per kilogram,

00:58:48.270 --> 00:58:50.420 align:middle line:90%
over a 1 gram average of tissue.

00:58:50.420 --> 00:58:53.670 align:middle line:84%
So the limit for the USA is more
stringent than for the European

00:58:53.670 --> 00:58:55.640 align:middle line:84%
Union, but other
countries around the world

00:58:55.640 --> 00:59:00.482 align:middle line:84%
such as Australia, New Zealand,
use the European limit.

00:59:00.482 --> 00:59:03.140 align:middle line:84%
NARRATOR: Some of the most
popular phones on the market

00:59:03.140 --> 00:59:07.600 align:middle line:84%
emit so much microwave
radiation that the SAR rating is

00:59:07.600 --> 00:59:08.720 align:middle line:90%
right on the edge of the limit.

00:59:08.720 --> 00:59:21.788 align:middle line:90%


00:59:21.788 --> 00:59:24.873 align:middle line:84%
Every millimeter of skull
helps protect the brain

00:59:24.873 --> 00:59:26.765 align:middle line:84%
against the phone's
microwave radiation

00:59:26.765 --> 00:59:31.030 align:middle line:84%
and therefore lowers
the phone's SAR rating.

00:59:31.030 --> 00:59:33.730 align:middle line:84%
Children get their first
phone at the average age

00:59:33.730 --> 00:59:34.930 align:middle line:90%
of eight years old.

00:59:34.930 --> 00:59:38.380 align:middle line:84%
An eight-year-old skull is
considerably thinner than that

00:59:38.380 --> 00:59:41.750 align:middle line:84%
of an adult. So you would
hope that phones are tested

00:59:41.750 --> 00:59:43.738 align:middle line:84%
against the skull which
represents the thickness

00:59:43.738 --> 00:59:45.232 align:middle line:90%
of that of a child.

00:59:45.232 --> 00:59:48.070 align:middle line:90%


00:59:48.070 --> 00:59:51.780 align:middle line:84%
The SAM head is an average
shaped and sized human skull.

00:59:51.780 --> 00:59:55.280 align:middle line:90%


00:59:55.280 --> 00:59:58.656 align:middle line:84%
The average of 10,000 people
has been taken in terms

00:59:58.656 --> 01:00:00.888 align:middle line:84%
of their head
measurements and this SAM

01:00:00.888 --> 01:00:02.840 align:middle line:84%
phantom head has
been created, which

01:00:02.840 --> 01:00:05.280 align:middle line:90%
is an average human skull.

01:00:05.280 --> 01:00:08.208 align:middle line:90%


01:00:08.208 --> 01:00:10.220 align:middle line:84%
NARRATOR: Obviously the
head of an average human

01:00:10.220 --> 01:00:12.230 align:middle line:84%
being is considerably
larger than that

01:00:12.230 --> 01:00:13.720 align:middle line:90%
