bigger, thicker head

01:00:45.874 --> 01:00:46.940 align:middle line:90%
than the average eight-year-old.

01:00:46.940 --> 01:00:49.760 align:middle line:90%


01:00:49.760 --> 01:00:52.850 align:middle line:84%
